<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>SSGPT6 Staff Media Vault</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
      background:#050910;
      color:#e5f7ff;
    }
    .container{width:min(96%,1100px);margin:40px auto;}
    h1{color:#00ffcc;letter-spacing:3px;font-size:1.6rem;}
    .grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));
      gap:18px;
      margin-top:20px;
    }
    .card{
      background:#0b1320;
      border:1px solid rgba(0,255,204,0.25);
      border-radius:12px;
      padding:14px;
    }
    .card h3{margin:8px 0;font-size:1rem;color:#00ffcc;}
    .meta{font-size:0.75rem;color:#9fb6c8;margin-bottom:6px;}
    .tag{
      display:inline-block;
      padding:3px 8px;
      border-radius:999px;
      border:1px solid rgba(0,255,204,0.4);
      font-size:0.7rem;
      color:#00ffcc;
      margin-top:6px;
    }
    .notice{
      margin-top:24px;
      font-size:0.8rem;
      color:#9fb6c8;
      border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      padding-top:14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>SSGPT6 STAFF MEDIA VAULT</h1>
    <p class="meta">
      Status: AUTHENTICATED · Owner: GNAIAAAC LLC (Institutional Use Only)
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.1rem;margin-top:24px;">Video Assets</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>energy-harvest-unit012.mp4</h3>
        <div class="meta">Category: Energy Harvesting · Status: AUTHENTICATED</div>
        <p>Technical demonstration of simulated multi-source energy extraction from thermal and vibration inputs.</p>
        <span class="tag">ENGINEERING PROOF</span>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>water-governance-pilot.mp4</h3>
        <div class="meta">Category: Water Governance · Status: AUTHENTICATED</div>
        <p>Walkthrough of an AI-assisted municipal water-stress simulation for governance and planning.</p>
        <span class="tag">GOVERNANCE MODEL</span>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>ssgpt6-voice-auth-demo.mp4</h3>
        <div class="meta">Category: Access Control · Status: AUTHENTICATED</div>
        <p>Demonstration of a voice-triggered interface authorizing secure document access.</p>
        <span class="tag">ACCESS CONTROL</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.1rem;margin-top:28px;">Photo Assets</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Infrastructure Asset 01</h3>
        <div class="meta">Type: Water Purification · Status: AUTHENTICATED</div>
        <p>High-resolution conceptual image of an industrial-scale water purification train (Unit 001).</p>
        <span class="tag">INFRASTRUCTURE</span>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Infrastructure Asset 02</h3>
        <div class="meta">Type: Solar-Wind Mesh · Status: AUTHENTICATED</div>
        <p>Wide-angle conceptual view of a solar-wind hybrid mesh installation (Unit 012).</p>
        <span class="tag">ENERGY NETWORK</span>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Architecture Asset 03</h3>
        <div class="meta">Type: System Blueprint · Status: AUTHENTICATED</div>
        <p>Blueprint-style visualization of the 135 Matrix showing how the AI Sleeping Agent connects every project.</p>
        <span class="tag">SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="notice">
      © 2026 GNAIAAAC LLC — All Rights Reserved. This media is proprietary to GNAIAAAC LLC and may not be reproduced,
      distributed, or used for commercial or institutional purposes without written authorization.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
